text: Lionel Funes Díaz (born 1 July 1968) is a Mexican politician from the National Action Party. In 2003 he served as Deputy of the LVIII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing the State of Mexico. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from the State of Mexico Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:National Action Party (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
